          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Restoring the Public Trust Act</b></p> <p>This bill sets forth provisions aimed at (1) prohibiting personal enrichment of federal employees, (2) rooting out conflicts of interest, and (3) increasing oversight and strengthening agencies responsible for rooting out corruption.</p>]]></text>
